## Problem 4: F1 Score

Suppose:

* Precision = 0.75
* Recall = 0.60

Find the **F1-score**.

### Solution

$$
F1=2\cdot\frac{\text{Precision}\cdot\text{Recall}}{\text{Precision}+\text{Recall}}
$$

Substitute:

$$
F1=2\cdot\frac{0.75\cdot0.60}{0.75+0.60}
$$

$$
F1=2\cdot\frac{0.45}{1.35}=\frac{0.90}{1.35}=0.667
$$

**Answer: 0.667**

