## Problem 29: Number of Parameter Updates

A training set has 1000 samples. Minibatch size is 100.

How many updates occur in one epoch?

### Solution

$$
\text{Updates per epoch}=\frac{1000}{100}=10
$$

**Answer: 10 updates**

